column33:
neighborhood app displayed 10-100 productions, all productions represents by row of html elements with color that choose by the ko/evocog group. 

when the rows have a lot of html element (it depend by the results) and when changing the amount of rows displayed by the slider input, this sometimes causes the page to stuck.

options for solving the problem:
1. display all the rows (100) in the first time and cancel the option to change the amount of rows in the screen by the slider, this solution displays the information after a very long time, so this solution is not good.

2. try to use virtual-scroll-component of Vuetify,  the virtual scroll component added display-none property to all rows baside that the rows that appear in the screen. when scrolling up and the down the virtual scroll changed dynamically the display property to None or Visible  to all rows as needed. 
this solution solve the issue, but it make another issue
When scrolling up and down, the change of display property dynamically causes scrolling to be slower.

Perhaps the best solution is to leave the page waiting to load when using the slider, however we will think of other solutions.;06/Aug/23 6:26 AM;nerias;72000
